Green Goddess Whipped Feta Dip
  --Stephanie Engoy

8 oz feta cheese, crumbled
1/4 c + 2 tbsp Greek yogurt
1/2 small avocado
1/2 c fresh herbs (parsley, basil, cilantro, and chives)
2 small garlic cloves
1 tbsp lemon juice
2 tbsp olive oil (plus more for drizzling)
Salt & pepper, to taste

Add all ingredients to a food processor and blend until smooth and creamy, scraping down the sides as needed. Adjust seasoning to taste and blend again until the color turns a vibrant green. Drizzle with olive oil and serve with a variety of crisp veggies and crackers or pita bread.


